Boulder Dash zaidimuko kompiliavimo-linkavimo taisykles.
Naudojant Kick3 neveikia komanda set

tai reikia daryti taip:

CC BOULDER.C +L
CC BOULDER2.C +L
CC CAVES.C +L
CC MUSIC.C +L

LN BOULDER.O BOULDER2.O MUSIC.O CAVES.O -lSYS1:lib/c32
                                          ^^^^^^^^^^^^
                                          tai PATH iki c32.library

P.S. Startup-Sequence ar kitur turi buti :
      ASSIGN INCLUDE: SYS1:include
   ir beto kai kurie include reikia pakeisti is <dermo/audio.h>
               i "INCLUDE:dermo/audio.h"

Su Pagarba Levui, Levas. 1995-Feb-12.

